## ğŸš€ Features

- Real-time fire detection using a custom YOLOv8 model  
- Multiple user-defined detection zones (ROI)  
- Zone-wise state machine (`SAFE â†’ FIRE â†’ CLEAR`)  
- Fire persistence validation to minimize false positives  
- MQTT-based integration for IoT / dashboards / automation  
- Supports laptop webcam and IP/CCTV (RTSP) cameras  
- Designed for industrial trials, demos, and monitoring systems  

